00:52:00,400 --> 00:52:01,992
<font color=#FFFF00>We need to keep moving.</font>

2203
00:52:02,840 --> 00:52:04,478
<font color=#FFFF00>We need to keep moving!</font>

2204
00:52:05,000 --> 00:52:08,549
<font color=#FFFF00>Everyone! Listen to me!
We need to keep moving!</font>

2205
00:52:08,800 --> 00:52:10,870
<font color=#FFFF00>If we stay idle, we all die.</font>

2206
00:52:11,680 --> 00:52:12,999
<font color=#FFFF00>Hands on oars!</font>

2207
00:52:13,400 --> 00:52:16,676
<font color=#FFFF00>Hands on oars! On my count!</font>

2208
00:52:17,000 --> 00:52:19,992
<font color=#FFFF00>And row!</font>

2209
00:52:20,760 --> 00:52:22,113
<font color=#FFFF00>And...</font>

2210
00:52:22,600 --> 00:52:23,749
<font color=#FFFF00>Row!</font>

2211
00:52:25,000 --> 00:52:26,274
<font color=#FFFF00>Together...</font>

2212
00:52:26,880 --> 00:52:29,075
<font color=#FFFF00>And row!</font>

2213
00:52:30,960 --> 00:52:32,313
<font color=#FFFF00>And...</font>

2214
00:52:32,920 --> 00:52:33,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Row!</font>

2215
00:52:35,640 --> 00:52:38,074
<font color=#FFFF00>And row!</font>

2216
00:52:41,120 --> 00:52:43,156
<font color=#FFFF00>And row!</font>

2217
00:52:43,240 --> 00:52:45,708
<font color=#FFFF00>Battering ram
on the starboard side!</font>

2218
00:55:30,200 --> 00:55:31,519
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala!</font>

2219
00:55:33,120 --> 00:55:35,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala, a notice has come
from the Ionian Sea.</font>

2220
00:55:35,760 --> 00:55:37,557
<font color=#FFFF00>The Astroea was lost in battle.</font>

2221
00:55:37,640 --> 00:55:39,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Greek rebels ambushed our ships.</font>

2222
00:55:40,560 --> 00:55:41,595
<font color=#FFFF00>Any survivors?</font>

2223
00:55:41,680 --> 00:55:43,398
<font color=#FFFF00>The entire third fleet is lost.</font>

2224
00:55:43,640 --> 00:55:45,358
<font color=#FFFF00>All are dead to the last man.</font>

2225
00:55:45,440 --> 00:55:47,351
<font color=#FFFF00>Caesar demands that we retaliate.</font>

2226
00:58:18,080 --> 00:58:20,469
<font color=#FFFF00>How long were you
a galley slave?</font>

2227
00:58:34,360 --> 00:58:36,078
<font color=#FFFF00>One never knows.</font>

2228
00:58:37,000 --> 00:58:40,356
<font color=#FFFF00>Dangerous territory.
Pirates and marauders.</font>

2229
00:58:41,480 --> 00:58:42,515
<font color=#FFFF00>And which are you?</font>

2230
00:58:43,200 --> 00:58:45,270
<font color=#FFFF00>The one not in chains.</font>

2231
00:58:47,400 --> 00:58:51,916
<font color=#FFFF00>You wash ashore shackled,
your back striped.</font>

2232
00:58:52,560 --> 00:58:55,028
<font color=#FFFF00>You were a galley slave. How long?</font>

2233
00:58:56,480 --> 00:58:57,879
<font color=#FFFF00>Five years.</font>

2234
00:58:58,320 --> 00:58:59,992
<font color=#FFFF00>What were you accused of?</font>

2235
00:59:00,680 --> 00:59:03,069
<font color=#FFFF00>- I committed no crime.
- And I lay no blame.</font>

2236
00:59:03,160 --> 00:59:05,993
<font color=#FFFF00>I asked what you were accused of.</font>

2237
00:59:07,400 --> 00:59:08,719
<font color=#FFFF00>Sedition.</font>

2238
00:59:09,080 --> 00:59:11,150
<font color=#FFFF00>That's a serious charge.</font>

2239
00:59:11,920 --> 00:59:13,560
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll have to turn you over to the Romans.</font>

2240
00:59:13,600 --> 00:59:14,999
<font color=#FFFF00>No. No.</font>

2241
00:59:15,080 --> 00:59:17,833
<font color=#FFFF00>You are an escaped prisoner.</font>

2242
00:59:17,920 --> 00:59:20,036
<font color=#FFFF00>To do otherwise would put
my camp in jeopardy.</font>

2243
00:59:20,280 --> 00:59:21,713
<font color=#FFFF00>They'll kill me.</font>

2244
00:59:22,680 --> 00:59:24,352
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure they will.</font>

2245
00:59:25,920 --> 00:59:28,070
<font color=#FFFF00>We will discharge him
outside the garrison</font>

2246
00:59:28,160 --> 00:59:29,388
<font color=#FFFF00>before we leave for Jerusalem.</font>

2247
00:59:29,480 --> 00:59:31,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Jerusalem.</font>

2248
00:59:31,200 --> 00:59:32,952
<font color=#FFFF00>That's where I'm from.</font>

2249
00:59:33,360 --> 00:59:34,998
<font color=#FFFF00>I have family there.</font>

2250
00:59:35,080 --> 00:59:37,833
<font color=#FFFF00>Your private affairs
are no concern of mine.</font>

2251
00:59:41,320 --> 00:59:43,436
<font color=#FFFF00>You race chariots?</font>

2252
00:59:43,520 --> 00:59:45,954
<font color=#FFFF00>Young men race chariots.</font>

2253
00:59:46,040 --> 00:59:49,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Old men wager on young men
who race chariots.</font>

2254
00:59:49,880 --> 00:59:52,792
<font color=#FFFF00>How will you race
with only three horses?</font>

2255
00:59:54,960 --> 00:59:56,916
<font color=#FFFF00>Aliyah is sick, but that's my dilemma.</font>

2256
00:59:57,000 --> 00:59:58,956
<font color=#FFFF00>No. She's dying.</font>

2257
00:59:59,760 --> 01:00:01,432
<font color=#FFFF00>I can help her.</font>

2258
01:00:02,160 --> 01:00:03,798
<font color=#FFFF00>I know horses.</font>

2259
01:00:04,120 --> 01:00:07,192
<font color=#FFFF00>I've seen it before. It's called farcy.</font>

2260
01:00:07,720 --> 01:00:10,075
<font color=#FFFF00>It can be treated with charcoal.</font>

2261
01:00:11,000 --> 01:00:12,513
<font color=#FFFF00>I can help her.</font>

2262
01:00:14,480 --> 01:00:16,835
<font color=#FFFF00>All I ask in return,</font>

2263
01:00:16,920 --> 01:00:18,558
<font color=#FFFF00>take me with you.</font>

2264
01:00:19,240 --> 01:00:20,992
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me find my family.</font>

2265
01:00:22,000 --> 01:00:23,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Or at least let me find out
what happened to them.</font>

2266
01:00:40,600 --> 01:00:42,272
<font color=#FFFF00>What is your name?</font>

2267
01:00:43,600 --> 01:00:44,749
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah.</font>

2268
01:00:45,760 --> 01:00:47,273
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah Ben-Hur.</font>

2269
01:00:49,840 --> 01:00:52,513
<font color=#FFFF00>The bargain is this, Judah Ben-Hur.</font>

2270
01:00:54,000 --> 01:00:56,195
<font color=#FFFF00>You owe me your life.</font>

2271
01:00:57,000 --> 01:00:59,560
<font color=#FFFF00>I expect that bill to be paid.</font>

2272
01:01:01,760 --> 01:01:03,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Release him.</font>

2273
01:01:14,960 --> 01:01:16,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Kill the leper!</font>

2274
01:01:21,720 --> 01:01:23,073
<font color=#FFFF00>Look at yourself!</font>

2275
01:01:24,880 --> 01:01:26,313
<font color=#FFFF00>Kill the leper!</font>

2276
01:01:31,480 --> 01:01:33,038
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't! Please don't!</font>

2277
01:01:34,400 --> 01:01:36,356
<font color=#FFFF00>- This man is your neighbor.
- Wait!</font>

2278
01:01:36,520 --> 01:01:38,397
<font color=#FFFF00>- The Torah tells us to...
- Wait! Stop!</font>

2279
01:01:38,480 --> 01:01:40,550
<font color=#FFFF00>...love your neighbor
as we love ourselves.</font>

2280
01:01:41,800 --> 01:01:43,916
<font color=#FFFF00>Wait. Stop! Stop!</font>

2281
01:01:44,000 --> 01:01:45,353
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop. Stop.</font>

2282
01:01:59,360 --> 01:02:02,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Hate, anger, fear.</font>

2283
01:02:02,760 --> 01:02:05,399
<font color=#FFFF00>Those are lies they
use to turn you against each other.</font>

2284
01:02:08,440 --> 01:02:11,716
<font color=#FFFF00>When you set aside the hate
they force you to carry,</font>

2285
01:02:12,320 --> 01:02:14,072
<font color=#FFFF00>that's when you know</font>

2286
01:02:14,600 --> 01:02:16,556
<font color=#FFFF00>love is our true nature.</font>

2287
01:02:19,400 --> 01:02:21,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you see what's
happening here?</font>

2288
01:02:23,200 --> 01:02:26,795
<font color=#FFFF00>Mark my words, Messala,
this is the poison.</font>

2289
01:02:27,560 --> 01:02:31,348
<font color=#FFFF00>But that man offers
the people something more,</font>

2290
01:02:31,440 --> 01:02:33,829
<font color=#FFFF00>and calms them with compassion.</font>

2291
01:02:33,920 --> 01:02:35,990
<font color=#FFFF00>This Jesus of Nazareth</font>

2292
01:02:36,080 --> 01:02:39,277
<font color=#FFFF00>is more dangerous
than all of the Zealots combined.</font>

2293
01:02:42,440 --> 01:02:44,396
<font color=#FFFF00>Wake up. Come on.</font>

2294
01:02:44,480 --> 01:02:46,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Up we go, come on. Up. Up.</font>

2295
01:02:48,240 --> 01:02:51,038
<font color=#FFFF00>Up we go. Good girl.</font>

2296
01:02:51,160 --> 01:02:53,196
<font color=#FFFF00>Up we go. Come on. Come on.</font>

2297
01:02:55,240 --> 01:02:56,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Ilderim.</font>

2298
01:02:56,720 --> 01:02:59,553
<font color=#FFFF00>Good girl. Good girl.</font>

2299
01:03:00,560 --> 01:03:03,677
<font color=#FFFF00>Good girl. Here we are.</font>

2300
01:03:04,360 --> 01:03:05,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Here we are.</font>

2301
01:03:07,400 --> 01:03:08,833
<font color=#FFFF00>Good girl.</font>

2302
01:03:11,320 --> 01:03:13,675
<font color=#FFFF00>She looks well.</font>

2303
01:03:14,760 --> 01:03:16,318
<font color=#FFFF00>No, not yet.</font>

2304
01:03:16,400 --> 01:03:18,789
<font color=#FFFF00>She is taking the charcoal, though.</font>

2305
01:03:18,880 --> 01:03:20,552
<font color=#FFFF00>Very nice.</font>

2306
01:03:21,600 --> 01:03:22,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Aliyah.</font>

2307
01:03:24,040 --> 01:03:25,359
<font color=#FFFF00>I had one just like her.</font>

2308
01:03:26,200 --> 01:03:28,316
<font color=#FFFF00>- Did you now?
- Yes.</font>

2309
01:03:29,520 --> 01:03:31,988
<font color=#FFFF00>So you do know something about horses.</font>

2310
01:03:32,840 --> 01:03:33,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Thank you,</font>

2311
01:03:35,080 --> 01:03:36,513
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah Ben-Hur.</font>

2312
01:03:56,720 --> 01:03:58,560
<font color=#FFFF00>They're harnessed wrong.
Aliyah should be here.</font>

2313
01:03:59,720 --> 01:04:00,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Kadeem?</font>

2314
01:04:01,200 --> 01:04:02,952
<font color=#FFFF00>Mind your business.</font>

2315
01:04:03,800 --> 01:04:05,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Listen to me.
If you take them into a gallop...</font>

2316
01:04:07,120 --> 01:04:08,792
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah.</font>

2317
01:04:08,880 --> 01:04:10,598
<font color=#FFFF00>...they're going to bolt.</font>

2318
01:04:25,560 --> 01:04:27,949
<font color=#FFFF00>The horses! Get the horses!</font>

2319
01:04:28,800 --> 01:04:29,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop those horses!</font>

2320
01:04:29,880 --> 01:04:31,560
<font color=#FFFF00>- Stay away! Stay away!
- Hold it! Hold it!</font>

2321
01:04:31,760 --> 01:04:32,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Ilderim, be careful.</font>

2322
01:04:33,080 --> 01:04:34,672
<font color=#FFFF00>Ilderim, move out of the way!</font>

2323
01:04:34,880 --> 01:04:36,233
<font color=#FFFF00>Whoa, now! Whoa!</font>

2324
01:04:37,760 --> 01:04:38,795
<font color=#FFFF00>Get out of the way!</font>

2325
01:04:43,600 --> 01:04:44,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Kadeem!</font>

2326
01:04:45,040 --> 01:04:46,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Aliyah!</font>

2327
01:04:46,280 --> 01:04:48,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop! Stop! Stop her!</font>

2328
01:04:49,760 --> 01:04:51,512
<font color=#FFFF00>- Kadeem!
- Hold it! Hold it!</font>

2329
01:04:52,240 --> 01:04:53,673
<font color=#FFFF00>- Aliyah!
- Judah, no!</font>

2330
01:04:53,760 --> 01:04:55,034
<font color=#FFFF00>Aliyah... Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!</font>

2331
01:04:55,160 --> 01:04:56,639
<font color=#FFFF00>No, Judah!</font>

2332
01:04:59,120 --> 01:05:00,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Hang on!</font>

2333
01:05:02,160 --> 01:05:03,718
<font color=#FFFF00>Whoa! Whoa! Whoa! Aliyah.</font>

2334
01:05:06,080 --> 01:05:07,308
<font color=#FFFF00>Here, take the reins.</font>

2335
01:05:11,080 --> 01:05:12,308
<font color=#FFFF00>Is she hurt?</font>

2336
01:05:12,400 --> 01:05:14,436
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh. Oh, Aliyah. Shh.</font>

2337
01:05:14,520 --> 01:05:15,555
<font color=#FFFF00>It's all right.</font>

2338
01:05:15,680 --> 01:05:17,432
<font color=#FFFF00>- You're fine.
- Easy, girl. Easy.</font>

2339
01:05:20,560 --> 01:05:22,040
<font color=#FFFF00>- Easy, girl. Shh.
- How did you know?</font>

2340
01:05:22,760 --> 01:05:24,830
<font color=#FFFF00>I told him Aliyah should be on the inside.</font>

2341
01:05:25,120 --> 01:05:28,396
<font color=#FFFF00>She hasn't run in a while.
She couldn't keep the pace.</font>

2342
01:05:28,680 --> 01:05:31,148
<font color=#FFFF00>When she broke stride,
she incited the others.</font>

2343
01:05:33,640 --> 01:05:34,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Kadeem.</font>

2344
01:05:34,680 --> 01:05:35,680
<font color=#FFFF00>How's he?</font>

2345
01:05:38,120 --> 01:05:39,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Not good.</font>

2346
01:05:48,160 --> 01:05:51,835
<font color=#FFFF00>How is it you weren't put
directly to the sword?</font>

2347
01:05:54,560 --> 01:05:56,471
<font color=#FFFF00>I was born to station.</font>

2348
01:05:56,840 --> 01:05:59,752
<font color=#FFFF00>A rich Jew sentenced to a slow death.</font>

2349
01:06:00,000 --> 01:06:03,390
<font color=#FFFF00>I imagine there were many in Rome who
found that very entertaining.</font>

2350
01:06:06,080 --> 01:06:09,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Was there ever a kind
more obsessed with the obscene?</font>

2351
01:06:11,120 --> 01:06:14,556
<font color=#FFFF00>People starve, the masses are enslaved,</font>

2352
01:06:14,920 --> 01:06:19,311
<font color=#FFFF00>and Caesar answers with
less bread and more circuses.</font>

2353
01:06:20,720 --> 01:06:22,517
<font color=#FFFF00>But I can't complain.</font>

2354
01:06:23,240 --> 01:06:26,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Their excessive nature lines my purses.</font>

2355
01:06:28,520 --> 01:06:30,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that why you're going to Jerusalem?</font>

2356
01:06:31,400 --> 01:06:33,994
<font color=#FFFF00>There'll be opportunities to race.</font>

2357
01:06:35,000 --> 01:06:39,278
<font color=#FFFF00>The Prefect is celebrating
himself with a tremendous circus</font>

2358
01:06:39,360 --> 01:06:41,715
<font color=#FFFF00>and his champion, Messala.</font>

2359
01:06:43,280 --> 01:06:44,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala Severus?</font>

2360
01:07:15,320 --> 01:07:16,936
<font color=#FFFF00>- I hope this keeps you warm.
- Thank you.</font>

2361
01:07:16,960 --> 01:07:18,598
<font color=#FFFF00>My love to your family.</font>

2362
01:07:19,160 --> 01:07:20,354
<font color=#FFFF00>- Thank you.
- God bless you.</font>

2363
01:07:23,000 --> 01:07:24,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Esther.</font>

2364
01:07:24,720 --> 01:07:27,951
<font color=#FFFF00>Good to see you, Simon. God bless you.</font>

2365
01:07:39,560 --> 01:07:41,278
<font color=#FFFF00>Esther, what is it?</font>

2366
01:08:05,400 --> 01:08:06,799
<font color=#FFFF00>My husband.</font>

2367
01:08:07,600 --> 01:08:09,158
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, I've missed you.</font>

2368
01:08:09,960 --> 01:08:11,951
<font color=#FFFF00>I've missed you so much.</font>

2369
01:08:17,680 --> 01:08:18,874
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, Judah.</font>

2370
01:08:25,680 --> 01:08:27,477
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah. Judah.</font>

2371
01:08:27,800 --> 01:08:28,915
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah.</font>

2372
01:08:39,800 --> 01:08:41,791
<font color=#FFFF00>I shouldn't have run.</font>

2373
01:08:41,880 --> 01:08:43,791
<font color=#FFFF00>They would have killed you, too.</font>

2374
01:08:44,280 --> 01:08:46,430
<font color=#FFFF00>I would have died with my family.</font>

2375
01:08:46,520 --> 01:08:49,512
<font color=#FFFF00>That's better than
being alone with my guilt.</font>

2376
01:08:50,120 --> 01:08:52,554
<font color=#FFFF00>I've filled my life in other ways.</font>

2377
01:08:53,840 --> 01:08:55,159
<font color=#FFFF00>By serving others?</font>

2378
01:08:57,120 --> 01:09:01,159
<font color=#FFFF00>I've found people to care for.
People who care for me.</font>

2379
01:09:01,520 --> 01:09:03,670
<font color=#FFFF00>When I can, I spread the Word.</font>

2380
01:09:04,320 --> 01:09:05,958
<font color=#FFFF00>The message of Jesus.</font>

2381
01:09:06,640 --> 01:09:08,631
<font color=#FFFF00>That carpenter, he showed you kindness</font>

2382
01:09:08,720 --> 01:09:10,199
<font color=#FFFF00>when no one else would.</font>

2383
01:09:10,280 --> 01:09:13,352
<font color=#FFFF00>I've seen him do acts of grace so small,</font>

2384
01:09:13,440 --> 01:09:14,960
<font color=#FFFF00>but so much more than other people do.</font>

2385
01:09:15,040 --> 01:09:17,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Every day for five years
I asked myself the same questions.</font>

2386
01:09:18,680 --> 01:09:20,511
<font color=#FFFF00>What happened to you?</font>

2387
01:09:21,040 --> 01:09:23,679
<font color=#FFFF00>What happened
to my mother and sister?</font>

2388
01:09:28,040 --> 01:09:29,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Were they crucified?</font>

2389
01:09:41,200 --> 01:09:42,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are they buried?</font>

2390
01:09:44,000 --> 01:09:45,479
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know.</font>

2391
01:09:48,200 --> 01:09:49,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Someone must know.</font>

2392
01:09:54,280 --> 01:09:55,474
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala.</font>

2393
01:09:55,560 --> 01:09:57,516
<font color=#FFFF00>He's become the pride of Roman Judea.</font>

2394
01:09:57,600 --> 01:09:59,000
<font color=#FFFF00>He's the commander of the garrison,</font>

2395
01:09:59,080 --> 01:10:01,310
<font color=#FFFF00>races chariots in Caesar's name.</font>

2396
01:10:01,400 --> 01:10:02,400
<font color=#FFFF00>You couldn't go near him.</font>

2397
01:10:07,680 --> 01:10:09,272
<font color=#FFFF00>You won't go near him.</font>

2398
01:10:13,760 --> 01:10:14,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Get up.</font>

2399
01:10:15,320 --> 01:10:16,976
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't stay in Jerusalem.
This isn't the place...</font>

2400
01:10:17,000 --> 01:10:19,696
<font color=#FFFF00>No, no, no, I'm safe. I'm staying
in a cabin outside the garden gate.</font>

2401
01:10:19,720 --> 01:10:22,029
<font color=#FFFF00>I will find
a way for us if that's what you still want.</font>

2402
01:10:22,760 --> 01:10:24,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Wait to hear from me.</font>

2403
01:10:25,320 --> 01:10:26,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah?</font>

2404
01:10:28,080 --> 01:10:30,992
<font color=#FFFF00>So, charlatans,
religious indoctrinators,</font>

2405
01:10:31,280 --> 01:10:32,554
<font color=#FFFF00>holy men.</font>

2406
01:10:32,640 --> 01:10:34,631
<font color=#FFFF00>We will work with local people.</font>

2407
01:10:34,720 --> 01:10:36,756
<font color=#FFFF00>We will make arrests.</font>

2408
01:10:37,480 --> 01:10:40,278
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyone who doesn't get the message,</font>

2409
01:10:40,360 --> 01:10:42,112
<font color=#FFFF00>we'll find an answer for.</font>

2410
01:10:42,200 --> 01:10:43,200
<font color=#FFFF00>What's this?</font>

2411
01:10:43,280 --> 01:10:46,511
<font color=#FFFF00>A gift brought by a messenger
with an invitation to meet.</font>

2412
01:10:46,600 --> 01:10:49,068
<font color=#FFFF00>- Meet where?
- He said you would know.</font>

2413
01:10:50,400 --> 01:10:52,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Have no fear of the Zealots.</font>

2414
01:10:54,400 --> 01:10:56,755
<font color=#FFFF00>They fight, they disrupt.</font>

2415
01:12:31,560 --> 01:12:33,630
<font color=#FFFF00>I haven't changed that much,
have I, brother?</font>

2416
01:12:35,800 --> 01:12:37,313
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you want?</font>

2417
01:12:39,280 --> 01:12:40,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Where is my mother and sister?</font>

2418
01:12:41,520 --> 01:12:42,999
<font color=#FFFF00>They're dead.</font>

2419
01:12:44,520 --> 01:12:46,317
<font color=#FFFF00>It was a quick death?</font>

2420
01:12:49,480 --> 01:12:51,357
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are they buried?</font>

2421
01:12:51,920 --> 01:12:54,195
<font color=#FFFF00>You forced my hand, Judah.</font>

2422
01:12:54,720 --> 01:12:56,995
<font color=#FFFF00>You chose the Zealots over me.</font>

2423
01:12:57,080 --> 01:12:58,991
<font color=#FFFF00>Listen, Judah, your pride...</font>

2424
01:12:59,080 --> 01:13:00,593
<font color=#FFFF00>Onwards! Quickly!</font>

2425
01:13:01,120 --> 01:13:02,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Surround this house!</font>

2426
01:13:02,640 --> 01:13:03,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Walk through the portal!</font>

2427
01:13:03,720 --> 01:13:04,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Coward.</font>

2428
01:13:07,360 --> 01:13:08,793
<font color=#FFFF00>Catch him! Do not let him escape!</font>

2429
01:14:03,600 --> 01:14:04,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Esther.</font>

2430
01:14:23,520 --> 01:14:25,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Faith brought you back to me.</font>

2431
01:14:26,920 --> 01:14:29,434
<font color=#FFFF00>The same faith that kept you alive.</font>

2432
01:14:30,120 --> 01:14:31,792
<font color=#FFFF00>That wasn't faith.</font>

2433
01:14:34,360 --> 01:14:36,476
<font color=#FFFF00>Faith wasn't strong enough.</font>

2434
01:14:36,600 --> 01:14:38,079
<font color=#FFFF00>That was hate.</font>

2435
01:14:38,720 --> 01:14:40,278
<font color=#FFFF00>I became hate.</font>

2436
01:14:42,680 --> 01:14:44,716
<font color=#FFFF00>That's what kept me alive.</font>

2437
01:14:50,080 --> 01:14:51,911
<font color=#FFFF00>Let Messala go.</font>

2438
01:14:53,120 --> 01:14:56,715
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you see
we've been given a second chance?</font>

2439
01:14:57,360 --> 01:15:00,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Spend it on hatred,
then you're still a slave.</font>

2440
01:15:02,760 --> 01:15:04,557
<font color=#FFFF00>What else do I have?</font>

2441
01:15:07,440 --> 01:15:08,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Me.</font>

2442
01:15:10,160 --> 01:15:11,718
<font color=#FFFF00>You have me.</font>

2443
01:15:15,840 --> 01:15:17,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala was down
when we entered.</font>

2444
01:15:17,920 --> 01:15:21,515
<font color=#FFFF00>There was at least one man.
He escaped over this balcony.</font>

2445
01:15:23,120 --> 01:15:25,031
<font color=#FFFF00>Were they Zealots?</font>

2446
01:15:25,120 --> 01:15:26,997
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know, Prefect.</font>

2447
01:15:39,720 --> 01:15:41,711
<font color=#FFFF00>And at the house of Hur.</font>

2448
01:15:48,280 --> 01:15:49,872
<font color=#FFFF00>You were in uniform.</font>

2449
01:15:50,880 --> 01:15:54,031
<font color=#FFFF00>An attack on you is an attack on Rome.</font>

2450
01:15:56,280 --> 01:15:58,396
<font color=#FFFF00>An example needs to be made.</font>

2451
01:15:59,400 --> 01:16:01,960
<font color=#FFFF00>What's the value of a Jew to a Roman?</font>

2452
01:16:04,960 --> 01:16:06,109
<font color=#FFFF00>Ten to one.</font>

2453
01:16:11,120 --> 01:16:13,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Twenty, I would say.</font>

2454
01:16:14,760 --> 01:16:16,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Pull twenty Jews from the streets.</font>

2455
01:16:17,880 --> 01:16:20,314
<font color=#FFFF00>Execute them
in the name of the Emperor.</font>

2456
01:16:22,280 --> 01:16:24,635
<font color=#FFFF00>And let the people know, Messala,</font>

2457
01:16:25,280 --> 01:16:27,271
<font color=#FFFF00>the days of forgiveness are behind them.</font>

2458
01:16:32,720 --> 01:16:34,278
<font color=#FFFF00>Five, six, seven, eight, nine,</font>

2459
01:16:34,400 --> 01:16:36,789
<font color=#FFFF00>10, 11, 12, 13, 14, 15, 16...</font>

2460
01:16:36,880 --> 01:16:38,096
<font color=#FFFF00>What are doing?
We've done nothing!</font>

2461
01:16:38,120 --> 01:16:39,416
<font color=#FFFF00>- Marcus!
- ...17, 18, 19.</font>

2462
01:16:39,440 --> 01:16:41,078
<font color=#FFFF00>I have two!</font>

2463
01:16:41,200 --> 01:16:44,237
<font color=#FFFF00>We have 19! Take one, leave the other!</font>

2464
01:16:51,200 --> 01:16:52,315
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah!</font>

2465
01:16:53,160 --> 01:16:54,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Have you been to the hillside?</font>

2466
01:16:54,920 --> 01:16:56,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Have you seen the twenty
they've crucified?</font>

2467
01:16:56,840 --> 01:16:58,114
<font color=#FFFF00>What twenty?</font>

2468
01:16:58,200 --> 01:17:01,158
<font color=#FFFF00>There's talk. A Roman
attacked at the house of Hur.</font>

2469
01:17:01,840 --> 01:17:02,909
<font color=#FFFF00>You did that.</font>

2470
01:17:03,000 --> 01:17:04,400
<font color=#FFFF00>If people are dead, that's on Rome.</font>

2471
01:17:04,480 --> 01:17:05,754
<font color=#FFFF00>You tried to kill Messala.</font>

2472
01:17:05,960 --> 01:17:08,793
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you to stay away from him, Judah.
I warned you!</font>

2473
01:17:09,120 --> 01:17:11,873
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't let him
go unpunished for what he's done to us.</font>

2474
01:17:11,960 --> 01:17:12,995
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't.</font>

2475
01:17:13,080 --> 01:17:15,275
<font color=#FFFF00>I watched my father be killed.</font>

2476
01:17:15,400 --> 01:17:18,000
<font color=#FFFF00>I know what it's like to
want to take your feelings out on others.</font>

2477
01:17:18,440 --> 01:17:21,591
<font color=#FFFF00>They deserve justice
for what's happened to them.</font>

2478
01:17:25,320 --> 01:17:27,550
<font color=#FFFF00>There's nothing here for you anymore.</font>

2479
01:17:27,640 --> 01:17:28,834
<font color=#FFFF00>Nothing.</font>

2480
01:17:38,040 --> 01:17:40,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Know the world you live in, Judah.</font>

2481
01:17:41,480 --> 01:17:43,516
<font color=#FFFF00>The world you live in is Rome's.</font>

2482
01:17:44,400 --> 01:17:45,435
<font color=#FFFF00>Their laws.</font>

2483
01:17:46,440 --> 01:17:47,873
<font color=#FFFF00>Their power.</font>

2484
01:17:48,360 --> 01:17:50,999
<font color=#FFFF00>You cannot fight them in the streets.</font>

2485
01:17:51,440 --> 01:17:53,192
<font color=#FFFF00>But there is another way.</font>

2486
01:17:53,960 --> 01:17:55,313
<font color=#FFFF00>The circus.</font>

2487
01:17:57,480 --> 01:17:58,480
<font color=#FFFF00>In the circus,</font>

2488
01:18:00,520 --> 01:18:02,078
<font color=#FFFF00>there is no law.</font>

2489
01:18:03,240 --> 01:18:04,275
<font color=#FFFF00>There is no right,</font>

2490
01:18:05,440 --> 01:18:06,759
<font color=#FFFF00>no wrong.</font>

2491
01:18:07,240 --> 01:18:09,879
<font color=#FFFF00>What happens there is sport,</font>

2492
01:18:09,960 --> 01:18:11,154
<font color=#FFFF00>not vengeance.</font>

2493
01:18:11,880 --> 01:18:13,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Do as you please.</font>

2494
01:18:13,680 --> 01:18:16,956
<font color=#FFFF00>Give them a show,
the people will cheer you.</font>

2495
01:18:19,120 --> 01:18:22,430
<font color=#FFFF00>How pathetic it must be
when your sole motivator is greed.</font>

2496
01:18:23,400 --> 01:18:25,436
<font color=#FFFF00>You feed my beauties.</font>

2497
01:18:25,920 --> 01:18:27,876
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't think you know me.</font>

2498
01:18:28,840 --> 01:18:31,308
<font color=#FFFF00>Five years in the gut of a slave ship.</font>

2499
01:18:31,400 --> 01:18:33,231
<font color=#FFFF00>I know what motivates.</font>

2500
01:18:33,600 --> 01:18:35,795
<font color=#FFFF00>Five years of pain
after twenty of privilege,</font>

2501
01:18:35,880 --> 01:18:39,236
<font color=#FFFF00>and now you think you know
something about suffering.</font>

2502
01:18:40,600 --> 01:18:43,068
<font color=#FFFF00>Your situation is not unique, Judah.</font>

2503
01:18:44,280 --> 01:18:45,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Neither are you.</font>

2504
01:18:47,000 --> 01:18:49,639
<font color=#FFFF00>My son spoke up for liberation.</font>

2505
01:18:50,120 --> 01:18:51,792
<font color=#FFFF00>He was branded a rebel.</font>

2506
01:18:52,600 --> 01:18:56,718
<font color=#FFFF00>Dragged through the streets,
his throat slit like a hog.</font>

2507
01:19:00,360 --> 01:19:03,796
<font color=#FFFF00>I traveled my
"all Romans must die" phase,</font>

2508
01:19:03,880 --> 01:19:05,108
<font color=#FFFF00>same as you.</font>

2509
01:19:06,360 --> 01:19:08,430
<font color=#FFFF00>All Romans won't die.</font>

2510
01:19:09,520 --> 01:19:11,078
<font color=#FFFF00>They can't die.</font>

2511
01:19:11,800 --> 01:19:14,268
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't kill them quickly enough.</font>

2512
01:19:15,640 --> 01:19:19,076
<font color=#FFFF00>If Messala is the pride of Rome,</font>

2513
01:19:20,160 --> 01:19:21,798
<font color=#FFFF00>take their pride.</font>

2514
01:19:22,840 --> 01:19:24,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Beat him in their circus.</font>

2515
01:19:25,440 --> 01:19:28,034
<font color=#FFFF00>Give them a shame they will understand.</font>

2516
01:19:29,880 --> 01:19:31,552
<font color=#FFFF00>I was accused.</font>

2517
01:19:32,800 --> 01:19:34,472
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm meant to be dead.</font>

2518
01:19:34,960 --> 01:19:36,473
<font color=#FFFF00>They won't let me race.</font>

2519
01:19:37,000 --> 01:19:38,797
<font color=#FFFF00>They're Romans, Judah.</font>

2520
01:19:40,480 --> 01:19:43,631
<font color=#FFFF00>For the right price,
they'll let you do anything.</font>

2521
01:20:11,320 --> 01:20:14,118
<font color=#FFFF00>I bring greetings
and congratulations</font>

2522
01:20:14,200 --> 01:20:16,111
<font color=#FFFF00>on the opening of your games, Prefect.</font>

2523
01:20:16,760 --> 01:20:19,035
<font color=#FFFF00>This is a private gathering,
old man. Move on.</font>

2524
01:20:19,680 --> 01:20:21,671
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not here to cause trouble.</font>

2525
01:20:22,320 --> 01:20:24,834
<font color=#FFFF00>Same as you, I'm here
for the love of sport.</font>

2526
01:20:26,800 --> 01:20:28,791
<font color=#FFFF00>So, where do I have to go to make a bet?</font>

2527
01:20:30,160 --> 01:20:31,195
<font color=#FFFF00>What's the wager?</font>

2528
01:20:31,840 --> 01:20:33,319
<font color=#FFFF00>My chariot.</font>

2529
01:20:35,760 --> 01:20:37,876
<font color=#FFFF00>The entries are long closed.</font>

2530
01:20:38,560 --> 01:20:40,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Three thousand gold pieces.</font>

2531
01:20:43,080 --> 01:20:45,230
<font color=#FFFF00>That enough to make you reconsider?</font>

2532
01:20:46,480 --> 01:20:49,153
<font color=#FFFF00>If that's not enough, how about this?</font>

2533
01:20:50,080 --> 01:20:52,833
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll give 3-to-1 odds on all bets.</font>

2534
01:20:55,880 --> 01:20:57,472
<font color=#FFFF00>My book is open.</font>

2535
01:20:58,400 --> 01:21:00,516
<font color=#FFFF00>That's very generous
against a strong field.</font>

2536
01:21:00,720 --> 01:21:02,756
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm not betting the field.</font>

2537
01:21:03,680 --> 01:21:07,434
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm betting that my driver
will be victorious over</font>

2538
01:21:07,520 --> 01:21:08,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala.</font>

2539
01:21:09,280 --> 01:21:11,635
<font color=#FFFF00>A bet like that's not customary.</font>

2540
01:21:11,760 --> 01:21:13,352
<font color=#FFFF00>And it's not appropriate.</font>

2541
01:21:13,440 --> 01:21:14,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Not appropriate for who?</font>

2542
01:21:15,480 --> 01:21:19,712
<font color=#FFFF00>All of those citizens who stand to
gain when you beat my man?</font>

2543
01:21:20,360 --> 01:21:22,590
<font color=#FFFF00>You will beat him, won't you?</font>

2544
01:21:22,760 --> 01:21:24,398
<font color=#FFFF00>He's just a Jew.</font>

2545
01:21:25,120 --> 01:21:27,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, I'm sorry. I failed to mention that.</font>

2546
01:21:28,080 --> 01:21:30,469
<font color=#FFFF00>But you've crushed an entire people.</font>

2547
01:21:30,560 --> 01:21:33,950
<font color=#FFFF00>I should think
crushing one man wouldn't be difficult.</font>

2548
01:21:34,200 --> 01:21:36,350
<font color=#FFFF00>You're on soft ground.</font>

2549
01:21:36,760 --> 01:21:38,113
<font color=#FFFF00>My money</font>

2550
01:21:39,000 --> 01:21:40,911
<font color=#FFFF00>against your pride.</font>

2551
01:21:42,000 --> 01:21:43,433
<font color=#FFFF00>Seems even.</font>

2552
01:21:46,560 --> 01:21:49,472
<font color=#FFFF00>3-to-1 not enough? How about 6-to-1?</font>

2553
01:21:50,800 --> 01:21:52,199
<font color=#FFFF00>With the agreement</font>

2554
01:21:52,920 --> 01:21:56,230
<font color=#FFFF00>that should my driver cross the line first,</font>

2555
01:21:56,320 --> 01:22:00,472
<font color=#FFFF00>any and all claims against him are quit.</font>

2556
01:22:01,840 --> 01:22:04,513
<font color=#FFFF00>Any, and all.</font>

2557
01:22:11,160 --> 01:22:12,309
<font color=#FFFF00>Good.</font>

2558
01:22:14,160 --> 01:22:16,276
<font color=#FFFF00>I will leave this with you</font>

2559
01:22:16,360 --> 01:22:17,918
<font color=#FFFF00>until the race is settled.</font>

2560
01:22:19,320 --> 01:22:21,470
<font color=#FFFF00>African! What's the name of the driver?</font>

2561
01:22:22,200 --> 01:22:23,872
<font color=#FFFF00>You know his name.</font>

2562
01:22:28,640 --> 01:22:29,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah!</font>

2563
01:22:29,720 --> 01:22:31,631
<font color=#FFFF00>Shorten those reins!</font>

2564
01:22:32,960 --> 01:22:34,393
<font color=#FFFF00>Go, go, go!</font>

2565
01:22:35,080 --> 01:22:36,308
<font color=#FFFF00>Go!</font>

2566
01:22:41,880 --> 01:22:43,108
<font color=#FFFF00>Step forward!</font>

2567
01:22:47,560 --> 01:22:48,879
<font color=#FFFF00>Good. Steady.</font>

2568
01:22:54,000 --> 01:22:55,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

2569
01:22:56,320 --> 01:22:57,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

2570
01:22:57,680 --> 01:22:59,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Good. It will get better.</font>

2571
01:22:59,200 --> 01:23:00,633
<font color=#FFFF00>I couldn't see anything.</font>

2572
01:23:01,160 --> 01:23:02,160
<font color=#FFFF00>In the circus,</font>

2573
01:23:02,520 --> 01:23:04,476
<font color=#FFFF00>be aware of the drivers' tricks.</font>

2574
01:23:04,560 --> 01:23:07,074
<font color=#FFFF00>Two riders part,
suck you in between them,</font>

2575
01:23:07,160 --> 01:23:08,957
<font color=#FFFF00>and crush you under their wheels.</font>

2576
01:23:09,040 --> 01:23:10,075
<font color=#FFFF00>It's called the "gate."</font>

2577
01:23:10,160 --> 01:23:11,957
<font color=#FFFF00>I just need to get to Messala.</font>

2578
01:23:12,040 --> 01:23:15,191
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, you think they're just
gonna give it to you?</font>

2579
01:23:16,760 --> 01:23:18,716
<font color=#FFFF00>No. The circus is a blood sport,</font>

2580
01:23:18,800 --> 01:23:19,994
<font color=#FFFF00>but it is sport.</font>

2581
01:23:20,080 --> 01:23:22,753
<font color=#FFFF00>There is strategy,
and you have to know it.</font>

2582
01:23:23,320 --> 01:23:24,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Good?</font>

2583
01:23:26,800 --> 01:23:27,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Esther.</font>

2584
01:23:31,840 --> 01:23:33,376
<font color=#FFFF00>Esther, I need to ask something of you.</font>

2585
01:23:33,400 --> 01:23:34,958
<font color=#FFFF00>There's nothing to speak of.</font>

2586
01:23:35,040 --> 01:23:36,712
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going to race Messala in the circus.</font>

2587
01:23:38,040 --> 01:23:39,871
<font color=#FFFF00>It's the only way to end this.</font>

2588
01:23:40,360 --> 01:23:41,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Please.</font>

2589
01:23:42,520 --> 01:23:45,159
<font color=#FFFF00>You always cared deeply for my family.</font>

2590
01:23:45,520 --> 01:23:47,078
<font color=#FFFF00>If you ever find their graves,</font>

2591
01:23:47,560 --> 01:23:50,597
<font color=#FFFF00>bury us together, put us all to rest.</font>

2592
01:23:50,840 --> 01:23:52,956
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah, you can't give up hope.</font>

2593
01:23:53,040 --> 01:23:55,235
<font color=#FFFF00>You must believe there's a better way.</font>

2594
01:23:57,240 --> 01:23:58,593
<font color=#FFFF00>There's not.</font>

2595
01:24:06,840 --> 01:24:08,592
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala rides like the devil.</font>

2596
01:24:09,680 --> 01:24:11,910
<font color=#FFFF00>He will do whatever he must to win.</font>

2597
01:24:18,480 --> 01:24:22,268
<font color=#FFFF00>Now, when you cut first,
they'll tend to put you up on one wheel.</font>

2598
01:24:22,360 --> 01:24:24,635
<font color=#FFFF00>So, you have to learn how to tilt.</font>

2599
01:24:24,720 --> 01:24:26,551
<font color=#FFFF00>It's all about balance, Judah.</font>

2600
01:24:26,640 --> 01:24:28,915
<font color=#FFFF00>It's a dangerous maneuver, of course,</font>

2601
01:24:29,040 --> 01:24:31,759
<font color=#FFFF00>but with courage and practice,
it can be mastered.</font>

2602
01:24:34,720 --> 01:24:36,995
<font color=#FFFF00>This is the spina.</font>

2603
01:24:37,800 --> 01:24:39,518
<font color=#FFFF00>This is where I'll be.</font>

2604
01:24:39,600 --> 01:24:41,192
<font color=#FFFF00>And I will try to guide you.</font>

2605
01:24:41,440 --> 01:24:45,752
<font color=#FFFF00>Now, when the race begins,
do not try to take the lead.</font>

2606
01:24:46,480 --> 01:24:50,234
<font color=#FFFF00>Lay back.
Let the other drivers fight for position.</font>

2607
01:24:50,760 --> 01:24:52,536
<font color=#FFFF00>- And the best strategy...
- But if I'm in the back,</font>

2608
01:24:52,560 --> 01:24:54,152
<font color=#FFFF00>how do I get to him?</font>

2609
01:24:54,240 --> 01:24:55,798
<font color=#FFFF00>The race will bring him to you.</font>

2610
01:24:56,800 --> 01:24:58,756
<font color=#FFFF00>With each successive lap,</font>

2611
01:24:59,920 --> 01:25:02,480
<font color=#FFFF00>there will be fewer and fewer chariots.</font>

2612
01:25:02,960 --> 01:25:06,157
<font color=#FFFF00>Which is why it's important
for you to stay back.</font>

2613
01:25:06,920 --> 01:25:10,151
<font color=#FFFF00>And remember, Judah, first to finish,</font>

2614
01:25:11,280 --> 01:25:12,952
<font color=#FFFF00>last to die.</font>

2615
01:25:21,440 --> 01:25:22,475
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala.</font>

2616
01:25:24,840 --> 01:25:26,034
<font color=#FFFF00>She wants you.</font>

2617
01:25:31,400 --> 01:25:34,233
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala! Messala!</font>

2618
01:25:34,320 --> 01:25:35,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Calm down.</font>

2619
01:25:35,440 --> 01:25:38,398
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala! Messala! Messala!</font>

2620
01:25:38,680 --> 01:25:40,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala! Messala!</font>

2621
01:25:46,440 --> 01:25:47,634
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't race him.</font>

2622
01:25:49,200 --> 01:25:50,679
<font color=#FFFF00>There's no stopping it.</font>

2623
01:25:51,040 --> 01:25:53,474
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm asking you to remember
that Judah is your brother.</font>

2624
01:25:54,080 --> 01:25:55,752
<font color=#FFFF00>The Hurs are your family.</font>

2625
01:25:55,840 --> 01:25:57,273
<font color=#FFFF00>My past is lost to me.</font>

2626
01:25:59,240 --> 01:26:01,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Each one of us has a choice.</font>

2627
01:26:03,440 --> 01:26:05,237
<font color=#FFFF00>You and Judah can make things right.</font>

2628
01:26:05,600 --> 01:26:06,874
<font color=#FFFF00>How?</font>

2629
01:26:06,960 --> 01:26:08,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Disqualify him,</font>

2630
01:26:08,280 --> 01:26:10,032
<font color=#FFFF00>or, disqualify yourself.</font>

2631
01:26:11,240 --> 01:26:13,879
<font color=#FFFF00>And be branded as a coward?
I'll die first.</font>

2632
01:26:14,400 --> 01:26:17,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, one of you will die.</font>

2633
01:26:18,200 --> 01:26:20,395
<font color=#FFFF00>There is no victory in this.</font>

2634
01:26:20,760 --> 01:26:23,911
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, so, you've come
to ask for my public humiliation.</font>

2635
01:26:24,760 --> 01:26:26,398
<font color=#FFFF00>No, Messala.</font>

2636
01:26:27,720 --> 01:26:30,234
<font color=#FFFF00>I've come to tell you
of the hell you'll unleash.</font>

2637
01:26:33,040 --> 01:26:35,554
<font color=#FFFF00>God punishes just as God forgives.</font>

2638
01:26:37,600 --> 01:26:39,636
<font color=#FFFF00>We have different gods.</font>

2639
01:26:39,720 --> 01:26:40,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Marcus!</font>

2640
01:26:41,840 --> 01:26:43,353
<font color=#FFFF00>She's asking for too much.</font>

2641
01:26:46,320 --> 01:26:47,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah.</font>

2642
01:26:49,840 --> 01:26:51,034
<font color=#FFFF00>Get up.</font>

2643
01:27:07,000 --> 01:27:08,228
<font color=#FFFF00>You recognize him?</font>

2644
01:27:13,720 --> 01:27:14,720
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

2645
01:27:14,760 --> 01:27:15,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Then he's a thief.</font>

2646
01:27:16,000 --> 01:27:17,672
<font color=#FFFF00>Take him, and give him a thief's reward.</font>

2647
01:27:17,760 --> 01:27:19,876
<font color=#FFFF00>No, Judah Ben-Hur.</font>

2648
01:27:22,120 --> 01:27:23,599
<font color=#FFFF00>You don't remember.</font>

2649
01:27:24,160 --> 01:27:25,991
<font color=#FFFF00>I remember you.</font>

2650
01:27:27,000 --> 01:27:29,275
<font color=#FFFF00>You never forget a man
who's held a knife to your throat.</font>

2651
01:27:29,360 --> 01:27:30,634
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll kill him!</font>

2652
01:27:30,720 --> 01:27:31,755
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll kill him! I swear!</font>

2653
01:27:32,800 --> 01:27:35,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Drusus. What's happened to you?</font>

2654
01:27:35,120 --> 01:27:37,236
<font color=#FFFF00>I know where your family is.</font>

2655
01:27:37,760 --> 01:27:40,149
<font color=#FFFF00>- My family are dead.
- No, they're not.</font>

2656
01:27:40,240 --> 01:27:41,355
<font color=#FFFF00>He's lying.</font>

2657
01:27:41,520 --> 01:27:43,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Rome doesn't keep prisoners,
it executes them.</font>

2658
01:27:44,040 --> 01:27:46,474
<font color=#FFFF00>Pilate ordered your family to be crucified,</font>

2659
01:27:46,560 --> 01:27:47,640
<font color=#FFFF00>but I had them intercepted.</font>

2660
01:27:48,040 --> 01:27:50,315
<font color=#FFFF00>Sent to the caves at Timnath-Serah.</font>

2661
01:27:50,800 --> 01:27:52,153
<font color=#FFFF00>Please, pay me,</font>

2662
01:27:52,440 --> 01:27:54,829
<font color=#FFFF00>and I can take you to your family.</font>

2663
01:27:58,080 --> 01:27:59,354
<font color=#FFFF00>I have to go with him.</font>

2664
01:28:00,800 --> 01:28:02,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Ilderim, you must allow me this.</font>

2665
01:28:02,520 --> 01:28:04,715
<font color=#FFFF00>I beg you. If there's even
a chance they're alive...</font>

2666
01:28:04,840 --> 01:28:06,114
<font color=#FFFF00>They are.</font>

2667
01:28:20,000 --> 01:28:21,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Let him up.</font>

2668
01:28:22,720 --> 01:28:24,278
<font color=#FFFF00>Prepare a horse for him.</font>

2669
01:28:31,520 --> 01:28:33,715
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll be back, I swear.</font>

2670
01:28:33,800 --> 01:28:35,791
<font color=#FFFF00>- Take this.
- What for?</font>

2671
01:28:35,880 --> 01:28:38,235
<font color=#FFFF00>He's a Roman.
That's all the reason you need.</font>

2672
01:29:07,720 --> 01:29:08,789
<font color=#FFFF00>Why would you save them?</font>

2673
01:29:08,880 --> 01:29:12,395
<font color=#FFFF00>I did it for Messala.
He cherished your sister.</font>

2674
01:29:12,480 --> 01:29:14,152
<font color=#FFFF00>If he wouldn't save her himself,</font>

2675
01:29:14,240 --> 01:29:16,435
<font color=#FFFF00>then I would save him
from his own mistake.</font>

2676
01:29:27,320 --> 01:29:28,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah, please, wait.</font>

2677
01:29:48,400 --> 01:29:49,594
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother?</font>

2678
01:29:52,880 --> 01:29:54,916
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, my God, you're alive.</font>

2679
01:29:56,520 --> 01:29:58,636
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother, it's me. It's Judah.</font>

2680
01:30:00,040 --> 01:30:01,393
<font color=#FFFF00>It's Judah.</font>

2681
01:30:04,120 --> 01:30:05,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah?</font>

2682
01:30:05,720 --> 01:30:07,119
<font color=#FFFF00>It's Judah.</font>

2683
01:30:08,680 --> 01:30:09,680
<font color=#FFFF00>It's your son.</font>

2684
01:30:21,640 --> 01:30:23,631
<font color=#FFFF00>I miss my boy.</font>

2685
01:30:24,800 --> 01:30:27,109
<font color=#FFFF00>- Mother, I'm here.
- No.</font>

2686
01:30:28,120 --> 01:30:30,475
<font color=#FFFF00>He's outside playing in the sun.</font>

2687
01:30:30,960 --> 01:30:33,315
<font color=#FFFF00>No, I'm Judah. I'm Judah.</font>

2688
01:30:34,720 --> 01:30:36,233
<font color=#FFFF00>You can't help us.</font>

2689
01:30:37,920 --> 01:30:39,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Tirzah, what's happened?</font>

2690
01:30:39,400 --> 01:30:41,311
<font color=#FFFF00>If you love us, forget about us.</font>

2691
01:30:41,400 --> 01:30:42,400
<font color=#FFFF00>What's happened?</font>

2692
01:30:42,480 --> 01:30:43,856
<font color=#FFFF00>- You are not my boy!
- Mother, what's wrong?</font>

2693
01:30:43,880 --> 01:30:44,880
<font color=#FFFF00>We're lepers. Get out.</font>

2694
01:30:45,000 --> 01:30:46,840
<font color=#FFFF00>- We're unclean, Judah!
- We're lepers!</font>

2695
01:30:46,920 --> 01:30:48,136
<font color=#FFFF00>- Get him out now!
- We're lepers!</font>

2696
01:30:48,160 --> 01:30:50,216
<font color=#FFFF00>- Get him out! Get him out!
- Judah, get out!</font>

2697
01:30:50,240 --> 01:30:51,514
<font color=#FFFF00>- Go away!
- Get him out!</font>

2698
01:30:51,600 --> 01:30:52,953
<font color=#FFFF00>You go away!</font>

2699
01:30:54,400 --> 01:30:56,152
<font color=#FFFF00>Gesius, they are dying. Let us take them.</font>

2700
01:30:57,000 --> 01:30:58,991
<font color=#FFFF00>- They have leprosy.
- Judah, please.</font>

2701
01:31:00,400 --> 01:31:02,231
<font color=#FFFF00>I did what I could. It's better this way...</font>

2702
01:31:02,320 --> 01:31:03,878
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll be back for them.</font>

2703
01:31:03,960 --> 01:31:05,896
<font color=#FFFF00>They're lepers,
they'd be stoned in the street!</font>

2704
01:31:05,920 --> 01:31:07,194
<font color=#FFFF00>I will be back for you!</font>

2705
01:31:09,320 --> 01:31:11,231
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah, I tried.
I saved them. I saved them!</font>

2706
01:31:11,360 --> 01:31:12,429
<font color=#FFFF00>You didn't save them!</font>

2707
01:31:12,520 --> 01:31:14,829
<font color=#FFFF00>You condemned them
to a life worse than death.</font>

2708
01:31:15,160 --> 01:31:16,878
<font color=#FFFF00>A life worse than death!</font>

2709
01:31:18,160 --> 01:31:20,390
<font color=#FFFF00>He'll pay for what he's done to us.</font>

2710
01:32:00,040 --> 01:32:02,395
<font color=#FFFF00>People of Jerusalem.</font>

2711
01:32:03,960 --> 01:32:06,076
<font color=#FFFF00>Friends of Rome!</font>

2712
01:32:06,280 --> 01:32:10,239
<font color=#FFFF00>We celebrate the power of man!</font>

2713
01:32:11,680 --> 01:32:13,159
<font color=#FFFF00>You idiot!</font>

2714
01:32:13,240 --> 01:32:14,389
<font color=#FFFF00>Get it now!</font>

2715
01:32:14,480 --> 01:32:16,277
<font color=#FFFF00>Men gathered here today</font>

2716
01:32:17,080 --> 01:32:19,594
<font color=#FFFF00>hailing from Persia,</font>

2717
01:32:20,720 --> 01:32:22,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Greece,</font>

2718
01:32:22,440 --> 01:32:23,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Arabia,</font>

2719
01:32:25,760 --> 01:32:27,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Syria...</font>

2720
01:32:28,240 --> 01:32:29,832
<font color=#FFFF00>...Ethiopia,</font>

2721
01:32:31,360 --> 01:32:32,713
<font color=#FFFF00>Egypt,</font>

2722
01:32:34,120 --> 01:32:35,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Judea.</font>

2723
01:32:42,080 --> 01:32:44,435
<font color=#FFFF00>And the unbeaten</font>

2724
01:32:44,520 --> 01:32:45,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Rome!</font>

2725
01:32:55,240 --> 01:32:57,834
<font color=#FFFF00>Going to run this. One time.</font>

2726
01:32:57,920 --> 01:32:59,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Good girl. Good girl.</font>

2727
01:32:59,920 --> 01:33:02,115
<font color=#FFFF00>We pay tribute to Caesar</font>

2728
01:33:02,920 --> 01:33:07,072
<font color=#FFFF00>and give thanks for his
virtue and his mercy</font>

2729
01:33:08,680 --> 01:33:10,716
<font color=#FFFF00>in this circus.</font>

2730
01:33:10,800 --> 01:33:14,634
<font color=#FFFF00>A grand arena, ten years in the making.</font>

2731
01:33:15,280 --> 01:33:17,510
<font color=#FFFF00>You will have the pleasure...</font>

2732
01:33:17,600 --> 01:33:20,068
<font color=#FFFF00>...for the first time in Judean history.</font>

2733
01:33:20,360 --> 01:33:21,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Ready?</font>

2734
01:33:21,440 --> 01:33:23,351
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't look so worried.</font>

2735
01:33:23,680 --> 01:33:26,148
<font color=#FFFF00>This wise old man once told me,</font>

2736
01:33:26,240 --> 01:33:28,800
<font color=#FFFF00>"First to finish, last to die."</font>

2737
01:33:29,160 --> 01:33:30,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Good advice.</font>

2738
01:33:36,760 --> 01:33:39,832
<font color=#FFFF00>You will see them race for glory.</font>

2739
01:33:40,400 --> 01:33:43,472
<font color=#FFFF00>You will see them fight for honor.</font>

2740
01:33:43,560 --> 01:33:45,915
<font color=#FFFF00>You will see them die for you!</font>

2741
01:34:08,400 --> 01:34:09,913
<font color=#FFFF00>You should have stayed away.</font>

2742
01:34:11,040 --> 01:34:12,792
<font color=#FFFF00>You should have killed me.</font>

2743
01:34:14,800 --> 01:34:16,028
<font color=#FFFF00>I will.</font>

2744
01:34:37,040 --> 01:34:40,589
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah! Judah! Pull back! Pull back!</font>

2745
01:34:42,040 --> 01:34:43,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!</font>

2746
01:34:46,400 --> 01:34:47,879
<font color=#FFFF00>What is going on?</font>

2747
01:35:10,320 --> 01:35:11,912
<font color=#FFFF00>Enjoy this lap!</font>

2748
01:35:13,160 --> 01:35:14,912
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll kill you on the next one!</font>

2749
01:35:48,800 --> 01:35:49,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Get back!</font>

2750
01:35:59,760 --> 01:36:00,909
<font color=#FFFF00>My helmet.</font>

2751
01:36:56,680 --> 01:36:57,795
<font color=#FFFF00>Hurry up!</font>

2752
01:37:30,720 --> 01:37:32,551
<font color=#FFFF00>The "gate," Judah! The "gate"!</font>

2753
01:37:40,200 --> 01:37:41,679
<font color=#FFFF00>Good move, Judah. Good move.</font>

2754
01:37:51,960 --> 01:37:54,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Another trick for you!</font>

2755
01:38:13,440 --> 01:38:14,634
<font color=#FFFF00>Fetch him! Fetch him!</font>

2756
01:38:16,800 --> 01:38:18,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Move him! Come on, move him!</font>

2757
01:38:18,520 --> 01:38:20,238
<font color=#FFFF00>Quick, get him on the rack.</font>

2758
01:38:25,600 --> 01:38:27,033
<font color=#FFFF00>Hurry up! Hurry up!</font>

2759
01:38:27,120 --> 01:38:28,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on! Come on.</font>

2760
01:38:28,200 --> 01:38:29,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Stand back! Stand back!</font>

2761
01:38:29,520 --> 01:38:31,033
<font color=#FFFF00>Hurry up! Move!</font>

2762
01:38:31,120 --> 01:38:33,270
<font color=#FFFF00>- Out of the way!
- Back up!</font>

2763
01:38:33,360 --> 01:38:34,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Get us up there!</font>

2764
01:38:34,720 --> 01:38:35,816
<font color=#FFFF00>- Move!
- Get out of the way!</font>

2765
01:38:35,840 --> 01:38:36,955
<font color=#FFFF00>Hurry!</font>

2766
01:39:04,000 --> 01:39:05,752
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll kill you!</font>

2767
01:39:07,840 --> 01:39:09,717
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you not Roman?</font>

2768
01:39:09,800 --> 01:39:11,711
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on, Messala!</font>

2769
01:39:40,400 --> 01:39:41,515
<font color=#FFFF00>Horses!</font>

2770
01:40:21,360 --> 01:40:22,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Go, Aliyah!</font>

2771
01:40:22,680 --> 01:40:23,795
<font color=#FFFF00>Go, go!</font>

2772
01:40:23,880 --> 01:40:26,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah! Judah! Judah! Judah!</font>

2773
01:40:28,400 --> 01:40:30,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah! Judah! Judah!</font>

2774
01:40:30,640 --> 01:40:31,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah! Judah!</font>

2775
01:40:43,520 --> 01:40:46,034
<font color=#FFFF00>- No shame to be second!
- We're riding now!</font>

2776
01:40:52,680 --> 01:40:53,908
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on! Come on!</font>

2777
01:40:54,000 --> 01:40:55,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on!</font>

2778
01:41:33,720 --> 01:41:35,551
<font color=#FFFF00>Are we having fun now, brother?</font>

2779
01:41:49,160 --> 01:41:50,593
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala!</font>

2780
01:42:00,840 --> 01:42:02,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah! Judah! Judah!</font>

2781
01:42:03,000 --> 01:42:04,797
<font color=#FFFF00>And row!</font>

2782
01:42:11,600 --> 01:42:12,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes!</font>

2783
01:42:13,400 --> 01:42:14,435
<font color=#FFFF00>Go!</font>

2784
01:42:19,240 --> 01:42:20,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Move!</font>

2785
01:42:26,080 --> 01:42:27,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Shorten up your reins, Judah!</font>

2786
01:42:31,320 --> 01:42:33,197
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah! Judah! Judah!</font>

2787
01:43:31,280 --> 01:43:32,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on, Judah.</font>

2788
01:43:41,400 --> 01:43:42,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Kill him!</font>

2789
01:43:43,240 --> 01:43:44,434
<font color=#FFFF00>Messala, kill him!</font>

2790
01:44:14,000 --> 01:44:15,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah!</font>

2791
01:44:34,320 --> 01:44:36,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah! Judah! Judah!</font>

2792
01:44:36,640 --> 01:44:37,993
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah! Judah!</font>

2793
01:44:38,360 --> 01:44:40,271
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah! Judah! Judah!</font>

2794
01:45:07,640 --> 01:45:09,596
<font color=#FFFF00>Wait. Wait!</font>

2795
01:45:36,520 --> 01:45:38,192
<font color=#FFFF00>Congratulations, African.</font>

2796
01:45:39,680 --> 01:45:40,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Take your winnings.</font>

2797
01:45:41,320 --> 01:45:42,992
<font color=#FFFF00>Condolences on your loss.</font>

2798
01:45:43,080 --> 01:45:44,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Loss?</font>

2799
01:45:46,040 --> 01:45:47,393
<font color=#FFFF00>Look at them.</font>

2800
01:45:48,920 --> 01:45:50,592
<font color=#FFFF00>They want blood.</font>

2801
01:45:52,040 --> 01:45:53,871
<font color=#FFFF00>They're all Romans now.</font>

2802
01:46:51,000 --> 01:46:52,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah?</font>

2803
01:46:53,040 --> 01:46:54,359
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

2804
01:46:56,480 --> 01:46:58,391
<font color=#FFFF00>You've won! You should be celebrating.</font>

2805
01:47:00,880 --> 01:47:02,836
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know what's ahead for us?</font>

2806
01:47:03,440 --> 01:47:06,432
<font color=#FFFF00>The riches we can make in Rome? Eh?</font>

2807
01:47:06,960 --> 01:47:10,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Wandering around the desert
with nothing, for nothing.</font>

2808
01:47:10,960 --> 01:47:12,518
<font color=#FFFF00>What kind of life is that?</font>

2809
01:47:12,960 --> 01:47:15,554
<font color=#FFFF00>It's something other than loneliness.</font>

2810
01:47:15,640 --> 01:47:17,676
<font color=#FFFF00>It's the only life I know.</font>

2811
01:47:35,360 --> 01:47:37,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Find something for yourself.</font>

2812
01:48:25,640 --> 01:48:26,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Peter.</font>

2813
01:48:45,160 --> 01:48:46,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Jesus!</font>

2814
01:48:46,480 --> 01:48:47,595
<font color=#FFFF00>Soldiers!</font>

2815
01:48:51,960 --> 01:48:54,110
<font color=#FFFF00>- Jesus of Nazareth...
- Stop!</font>

2816
01:48:54,200 --> 01:48:55,920
<font color=#FFFF00>In the name of Caesar,
you are under arrest.</font>

2817
01:48:57,480 --> 01:48:59,914
<font color=#FFFF00>Peter! Peter! No trouble.</font>

2818
01:49:00,200 --> 01:49:02,111
<font color=#FFFF00>Not from any of you.</font>

2819
01:49:02,440 --> 01:49:05,113
<font color=#FFFF00>Those who live by the sword,
will die by the sword.</font>

2820
01:49:10,080 --> 01:49:12,435
<font color=#FFFF00>Jesus! Jesus!</font>

2821
01:49:13,800 --> 01:49:15,836
<font color=#FFFF00>Dear Lord, please help us!</font>

2822
01:49:15,920 --> 01:49:17,717
<font color=#FFFF00>He's our Savior! Please let him go!</font>

2823
01:49:19,240 --> 01:49:20,639
<font color=#FFFF00>Please help!</font>

2824
01:49:21,440 --> 01:49:23,158
<font color=#FFFF00>Esther!</font>

2825
01:49:23,240 --> 01:49:24,514
<font color=#FFFF00>Esther!</font>

2826
01:49:25,240 --> 01:49:26,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Esther!</font>

2827
01:49:27,320 --> 01:49:29,754
<font color=#FFFF00>You heard him, stand back!</font>

2828
01:49:30,280 --> 01:49:31,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Esther?</font>

2829
01:49:33,160 --> 01:49:35,355
<font color=#FFFF00>Esther? Esther?</font>

2830
01:49:41,280 --> 01:49:42,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Impostor!</font>

2831
01:49:43,080 --> 01:49:45,275
<font color=#FFFF00>Move!</font>

2832
01:50:00,800 --> 01:50:02,438
<font color=#FFFF00>No water for him.</font>

2833
01:50:03,800 --> 01:50:05,313
<font color=#FFFF00>No water for him!</font>

2834
01:50:05,720 --> 01:50:08,109
<font color=#FFFF00>Drink. Please drink.</font>

2835
01:50:08,680 --> 01:50:10,238
<font color=#FFFF00>No water for him!</font>

2836
01:50:15,800 --> 01:50:16,994
<font color=#FFFF00>No, Judah.</font>

2837
01:50:18,840 --> 01:50:20,478
<font color=#FFFF00>My life,</font>

2838
01:50:20,560 --> 01:50:23,597
<font color=#FFFF00>I give it of my own free will.</font>

2839
01:50:46,360 --> 01:50:47,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Someone should help him.</font>

2840
01:50:49,280 --> 01:50:51,032
<font color=#FFFF00>I thought you were
the son of God!</font>

2841
01:50:56,280 --> 01:50:57,554
<font color=#FFFF00>Put him to death!</font>

2842
01:50:57,640 --> 01:51:00,359
<font color=#FFFF00>You'll get what you deserve!</font>

2843
01:51:14,600 --> 01:51:17,068
<font color=#FFFF00>We deserve to die
for our crimes!</font>

2844
01:51:17,480 --> 01:51:20,119
<font color=#FFFF00>But this man has done nothing wrong!</font>

2845
01:51:21,720 --> 01:51:22,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Jesus?</font>

2846
01:51:23,800 --> 01:51:26,712
<font color=#FFFF00>Remember me when you come
into your kingdom.</font>

2847
01:51:29,240 --> 01:51:33,392
<font color=#FFFF00>Today, you will be with me in paradise.</font>

2848
01:51:41,880 --> 01:51:43,199
<font color=#FFFF00>Father,</font>

2849
01:51:43,880 --> 01:51:45,359
<font color=#FFFF00>forgive them,</font>

2850
01:51:46,320 --> 01:51:48,754
<font color=#FFFF00>for they know not what they do.</font>

2851
01:52:03,080 --> 01:52:04,229
<font color=#FFFF00>It's</font>

2852
01:52:06,040 --> 01:52:07,040
<font color=#FFFF00>finished.</font>

2853
01:52:21,960 --> 01:52:23,109
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on.</font>

2854
01:52:23,600 --> 01:52:25,477
<font color=#FFFF00>That's it! Come on!
Let's move out!</font>

2855
01:52:36,760 --> 01:52:37,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Come on!</font>

2856
01:53:38,880 --> 01:53:40,029
<font color=#FFFF00>We're healed.</font>

2857
01:53:47,680 --> 01:53:48,874
<font color=#FFFF00>Judah...</font>

2858
01:54:00,360 --> 01:54:02,032
<font color=#FFFF00>How could this be?</font>

2859
01:54:06,920 --> 01:54:08,399
<font color=#FFFF00>I will take them.</font>

2860
01:54:12,040 --> 01:54:13,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Come.</font>

2861
01:54:13,520 --> 01:54:14,714
<font color=#FFFF00>You are free.</font>

2862
01:54:23,160 --> 01:54:24,991
<font color=#FFFF00>I lost him.</font>

2863
01:54:25,080 --> 01:54:26,479
<font color=#FFFF00>I've lost my brother.</font>

2864
01:54:26,560 --> 01:54:28,232
<font color=#FFFF00>No, you must have faith, Judah.</font>

2865
01:55:10,440 --> 01:55:11,953
<font color=#FFFF00>I see you.</font>

2866
01:55:15,640 --> 01:55:17,835
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't stand so far away. Come close.</font>

2867
01:55:20,720 --> 01:55:22,233
<font color=#FFFF00>Come see what you did to me.</font>

2868
01:55:23,880 --> 01:55:25,711
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't go that easy.</font>

2869
01:55:26,960 --> 01:55:29,190
<font color=#FFFF00>As long as I live, I'll claw at you.</font>

2870
01:55:29,280 --> 01:55:31,794
<font color=#FFFF00>And if I die, I'll drag you
beneath the ground beside me!</font>

2871
01:55:32,400 --> 01:55:34,630
<font color=#FFFF00>With the last of me,
I'll choke the life from you!</font>

2872
01:55:34,720 --> 01:55:35,720
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

2873
01:55:35,800 --> 01:55:37,320
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll make myself whole again, I swear,</font>

2874
01:55:37,360 --> 01:55:38,634
<font color=#FFFF00>and when I do, I'll kill you!</font>

2875
01:55:39,160 --> 01:55:40,878
<font color=#FFFF00>- No more killing.
- You did this to me!</font>

2876
01:55:40,960 --> 01:55:43,235
<font color=#FFFF00>- No more slaughter.
- You did this!</font>

2877
01:55:47,640 --> 01:55:49,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Remember when we were young?</font>

2878
01:55:51,000 --> 01:55:52,831
<font color=#FFFF00>When I was hurt and you carried me</font>

2879
01:55:53,480 --> 01:55:56,074
<font color=#FFFF00>with all your strength
for as long as you could.</font>

2880
01:55:56,880 --> 01:55:58,836
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't fight anymore.</font>

2881
01:55:59,160 --> 01:56:00,991
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't hate anymore.</font>

2882
01:56:04,840 --> 01:56:06,159
<font color=#FFFF00>All I can do is carry you.</font>

2883
01:56:13,880 --> 01:56:16,519
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, Judah, forgive me.</font>

2884
01:56:17,400 --> 01:56:18,958
<font color=#FFFF00>No, forgive me.</font>

2885
01:56:19,720 --> 01:56:21,153
<font color=#FFFF00>Forgive me.</font>

2886
01:56:29,520 --> 01:56:32,080
<font color=#FFFF00>There were
many miracles that day,</font>

2887
01:56:33,520 --> 01:56:35,317
<font color=#FFFF00>and in the days that followed.</font>

2888
01:56:37,960 --> 01:56:39,154
<font color=#FFFF00>As time passed,</font>

2889
01:56:39,920 --> 01:56:43,708
<font color=#FFFF00>forgiveness and understanding
had reunited the family.</font>

2890
01:56:48,520 --> 01:56:51,512
<font color=#FFFF00>To give hope and promise
for a better way.</font>

2891
01:56:52,400 --> 01:56:54,630
<font color=#FFFF00>To fight the good fight,</font>

2892
01:56:54,720 --> 01:56:55,720
<font color=#FFFF00>to finish the race,</font>

2893
01:56:57,720 --> 01:56:59,676
<font color=#FFFF00>to keep the faith.</font>

2894
01:57:12,120 --> 01:57:14,031
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't look back, J udah.</font>

2895
01:57:14,600 --> 01:57:16,397
<font color=#FFFF00>Your whole life is ahead of you.</font>

2896
01:57:20,920 --> 01:57:22,194
<font color=#FFFF00>You ready, brother?</font>

